The paper discusses privacy in a smart metering system, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also uses information theory (cs.IT) to study the privacy trade-off. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of energy harvesting and storage devices, which are related to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and emerging technologies (cs.ET).
